Motorball
FEEDBACK / bug-reports
Report bugs and weirdness here. How to submit a bug report: 1. Use the command ! bug (without the space). This only works in this channel. 2. Within the same message and on the same line, type a concise, good quality title for your bug report. You will get a DM from the bot to give more information if needed. 3. There is no upvote thresh-hold on bug reports. 4. If a bug reported in this channel is resolved, it will be posted here again as complete. There is no leaderboard for bug reports like in the other feedback channels. Troll/joke bug reports will be deleted and will result in a warning. Community board: https://open.codecks.io/motorball
